quran[31{c,v,t}:
79,16,jab is ke Rab ne ussay tawee ki muqaddas waadi mein puraka tha
79,17,"ke"" firaon ke paas ja, woh sarkash ho gaya hai"
79,18,aur is se keh kya to iss ke liye tayyar hai ke pakizgee ikhtiyar kere
79,19,"aur mein tairay Rab ki taraf teri rahnumai karoon to ( uss ka ) khauf tairay andar peda ho? """
79,20,phir moose ne ( firaon ke paas ja kar ) uss ko barri nishani dikhayi
79,21,magar uss ne jhutla diya aur nah maana
79,22,phir chalbaziyan karne ke liye palta
79,23,aur logon ko jama kar ke is ne pukaar kar kaha
79,24,""" mein tumhara sab se bara rab hon """
79,25,aakhir kaar Allah ne usay akhirat aur duniya ke azaab mein pakar liya
79,26,dar haqeeqat iss mein barri Ibrat hai har uss shakhs ke liye jo daray
79,27,kya tum logon ki takhleeq ziyada sakht kaam hai ya aasman ki? Allah ne uss ko banaya
79,28,uss ki chhat khoob onche uthai phir uss ka tawazun qaim kya
79,29,aur uss ki raat dhanki uss ka din nikala
79,30,iss ke baad zameen ko is ne bichhaya
79,31,uss ke andar se uss ka pani aur charah nikala
79,32,aur pahar is mein garh diye
79,33,samaan zeist ke tor par tumahray liye aur tumahray maweshion ke liye
79,34,phir jab woh hungama azeem barpaa hoga
79,35,jis roz ensaan apna sab kya dhara yaad kere ga
79,36,aur har dekhnay walay ke samnay dozakh khol kar rakh di jaye gi
79,37,to jis ne sar kashi ki thi
79,38,aur duniya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh di thi
79,39,dozakh hi is ka thikana hogi
79,40,aur jis ne apne Rab ke samnay kharray honay ka khauf kya tha aur nafs ko buri khwahisaat se baz rakha tha
79,41,jannat is ka thikana hogi
79,42,"yeh log tum se puchhte hain ke"" aakhir woh gharri kab aa kar thire gi? """
79,43,tumhara kya kaam ke is ka waqt batao
79,44,is ka ilm to Allah par khatam hai
79,45,tum sirf khabardaar karne walay ho har uss shakhs ko jo uss ka khauf kere
79,46,jis roz yeh log usay dekh len ge to inhen yun mehsoos hoga ke ( yeh duniya mein ya haalat mout mein ) bas aik din ke pichlle pehar ya aglay pehar taq thire hain
